Join The Student Wellness Hub for a workshop designed to provide Jewish students with a safe space to explore the impact of intergenerational trauma and rising antisemitism. Led by Dr. Tamara Soles, a psychologist and founder of The Secure Child Center for Families and Children, this session will include psychoeducation, group discussion, and empowerment exercises.
